      "role": "user",
      "content": "Interesting. You mentioned Candidate B \"uses slang\" and sounds \"too casual.\" If we look at the actual content of their answers, they are basically saying the exact same thing as Candidate A. Do you think the difference in how they speak actually affects their ability to solve the customer's problem, or is it just about the \"vibe\" of the language?",
